    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a fair-condition driver that would suit someone looking for an affordable, usable car rather than a fully sorted or show-ready example. It shows noticeable age and wear in the paint, interior, and overall presentation, with the kind of cosmetic flaws and imperfections you would expect from a car that has been used and enjoyed over time. That said, it still presents as a complete, serviceable vehicle for someone who values practicality and entry price over perfection. Buyers should expect an honest car with visible wear and some needs typical of a fair-condition example, but one that can still be a worthwhile option for the right person.",
