    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable, affordable transportation with honest character and plenty of value for the money. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-friendly option for buyers who want a practical car at an accessible price point. It shows its age and use, but it remains a solid opportunity for a commuter, first-time driver, or anyone looking for inexpensive wheels without unnecessary frills. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering real utility.",
