    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option that could be a great fit for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a parts donor. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is and offered by a seller who believes in being upfront and easy to work with. If you want something cheap with room to make it your own, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong-running powertrain and honest bones. Starts, drives, and has the kind of mechanical character enthusiasts look for, with a responsive engine, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and a chassis that feels like a worthwhile platform to sort and enjoy. Not a showroom example, but a budget-friendly driver/project with good parts value and plenty of upside for someone who knows their way around a toolbox. Priced to reflect condition while still offering real potential.",
      "price": 7900.0,
