    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of presence that makes every drive feel like the start of a story. It\u2019s an ideal candidate for someone who appreciates character, enjoys a hands-on project, or simply wants an affordable set of wheels with unmistakable charm. Whether you\u2019re looking for a budget-friendly runabout, a weekend tinkering companion, or a platform full of possibility, this one offers plenty of potential at a price that leaves room to make it your own.",
